children.subject: I can confirm I have the form. Thanks for submitting on time!
I submitted the form earlier this semester and have not received a confirmation mail. Is there a way to check if my form has been processed?

history.content:
Students who are graduating in Spring 2019 and completing the CS minor must complete Step 2 of the CS minor process by Friday, May 3 at 5PM. Failure to complete this step will result in not earning your minor. 

You must have your major advisor sign off on the Step 2 form, so plan in advance! Forms can be submitted to 349 Soda. If we're not around, you may slip the form under the door.
